On the other hand, sustaining the global GDP growth (Target 8.1) only (without combining it with Target 7.3) should not be considered as an ambitious target. Maintaining something that has already been achieved is just doing business as usual. Therefore, the energy equivalence of Target 8.1 (E8.1
                     ) is the total energy demand under the BAU. The total energy demand under the SDGs regime is the energy demand associated with the combination of Targets 8.1 and 7.3 (E8.1+7.3
                     ), which will be lower than E8.1
